title: Badass Women from TV Shows - Salute
author: S. O.
description:
TV's Badass Girls - Criminal Minds | Orphan Black | Person of Interest | The Blacklist | Vikings

A big Salute to all the Women Power on TV! 
This is a fanvid featuring my favourite characters of my favourite TV shows:
Criminal Minds - JJ and Prentiss (with a Tricia Helfer bonus)
Person Of Interest - Root and Shaw
Orphan Black - Sarah (and a little bit of Helena)
The Blacklist - Lizzie
Vikings - Lagertha

Song: Salute by Little Mix
All video clips belong to the series mentioned above and it's owner networks.
No Copyright infringment intended.
